# Git & Releases

## Commit messages

Use [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/) — enforced by commitlint and required for semantic-release:

```
feat: add E2E tests for contact modal
fix: resolve theme switcher flash on load
docs: update experience section copy
```

Allowed types: `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `style`, `refactor`, `perf`, `test`, `build`, `ci`, `chore`, `revert`.

## Releases

- semantic-release on `main` after CI passes
- `feat:` → minor, `fix:`/`perf:`/`revert:` → patch, `BREAKING CHANGE:` → major
- Do **not** manually edit `CHANGELOG.md`

## Deployment

- Cloudflare Pages: `yarn build` → `build/`
- Preview deploys on PRs; production on push to `main`
- Only commit when the user explicitly asks
